.DT
is_option
Disk World creator help
is_option

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
is_option -  This method checks to see if the specified option path exists.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int is_option(object player,
string name)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the player this is relative to
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the option path to check
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if it is an option, 0 if not
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/options_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method checks to see if the specified option path exists.  This
will only return true if it is an actual option, not an option group.
.EP

